## 🎯 Usage Examples

### Atom (Smallest)
```kotlin
BX3Button(
    text = "Submit",
    onClick = { },
    variant = BX3ButtonVariant.PRIMARY
)
```

### Molecule (Composed)
```kotlin
BX3InputField(
    value = state,
    onValueChange = { state = it },
    hint = "Enter email",
    validator = Validation.Email
)
```

### Organism (Complex)
```kotlin
BX3AIWidget(
    contextSnapshot = "Dashboard showing 3 tasks",
    onPrompt = { handleAI(it) },
    suggestedPrompts = listOf(
        SuggestedPrompt("Explain", "Explain the dashboard"),
        SuggestedPrompt("Refactor", "Refactor this code")
    )
)
```

### Template (Screen Layout)
```kotlin
BX3DashboardTemplate(
    title = "Dashboard",
    stats = listOf(stat1, stat2, stat3),
    navItems = listOf(NavItem(...)),
    currentRoute = "/dashboard"
)
```

